media:group.media:title: Earthbound's Most Mysterious Character
media:group.media:description:
Continuing on with some more Mother theory, today we are discussing the origins and purpose of one of Earthbound's most intriguing characters, Buzz Buzz. An extremely important character that doesn't have much in the way of screentime or dialogue, Buzz Buzz is a mystery indeed. 

Who do YOU think Buzz Buzz is?
